column5: I am renting a cottage on this Lake.  The owner tells me there are Pickerel and Bass and the info I have found(MNR,Guide to Eating Fish) confirms this.  Anyone ever fish this Lake? Any tips? or more info about Lake.  Thanks Rick
i fished it many moons ago and got some decent smallmouth.As i remember there was a HUGE rock in the middle of the lake,great for fish not so good for props.
AH! Mid Lake Hump!  Good to know always a Fish magnet and I agree not so good for props  Is this Rock marked at all?  Rick
Hey Rick shoot me a pm and i will give you some info on salmon trout
